titles.title: To inform the Senate that a quorum of the House had assembled and had elected Thomas S. Foley, a Representative from the State of Washington, Speaker, and Donnald K. Anderson, a citizen of the State of California, Clerk.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to by voice vote.

action.text: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

bill.summary: 1/5/1993--Introduced. Informs the Senate that a quorum of the House of Representatives has assembled, that Thomas S. Foley has been elected Speaker, and that Donnald K. Anderson has been elected Clerk.
